text: Please add support for the function 'PERCENTRANK'.
creator: chrisefr@gmail.com
apache@gagravarr.org
text:
Please see Yegor's ApacheCon talk for details on how to go about adding new functions to the formula evaluator:

http://people.apache.org/~yegor/apachecon_us2010/Evaluation_Of_Excel_Formulas_In_POI.pptx

Please do send in a patch if you get something working!

creator: onealj@apache.org
text:
https://support.office.com/en-us/article/PERCENTRANK-function-F1B5836C-9619-4847-9FC9-080EC9024442

This function looks like it is used to determine what percentile a given number is within a data set.
It also looks like it is an OOXML-only formula.
